üì± Core Benefits of the Social Media Pillar

1. Multi-Platform Post Scheduler

Draft once ‚Äî deploy across platforms (Facebook, X/Twitter, LinkedIn, Instagram, Threads, YouTube, etc.) on your schedule. Includes preview modes, time-zone adjustment, auto-captions, hashtag libraries, and queued content banks.

2. Live Engagement Dashboard

Monitor likes, comments, shares, replies, retweets, tags, and mentions from a unified screen. Highlight urgent items. Track comment trends. Tag internal responders. Archive everything in real-time.

3. Crisis Monitoring & Rapid Response

Set keyword triggers or alert phrases that notify your internal team when a post gains unexpected attention ‚Äî good or bad. Includes escalation flags, reply delay timers, and auto-freeze tools to temporarily pause content queues.

4. Security & Admin Lockdown Features

No more rogue posts or surprise lockouts. Assign specific bots, users, or captains to each account with different permissions. Auto-expire old logins, enforce password rotation, and store recovery keys locally.

5. Comment Moderation & Auto-Filter Controls

Set rules for profanity, hate speech, spam, or sensitive words. Auto-hide or flag suspicious content. All removals are logged and archived for audit protection.

6. Cross-Platform Hashtag Tracker

Track branded hashtags, industry tags, campaign keywords, or team-specific phrases across multiple platforms. Includes exportable reports and trend summaries.

7. Internal Notes & Post History Journal

Every post includes an internal-only note option for teams to explain strategy, timing, or response instructions. All edits, deletions, or re-shares are logged automatically.

8. Bot-Assisted Reply Drafting

Optional lightweight bots assist in drafting polite, brand-consistent replies to comments or DMs. You approve or modify replies before sending. No auto-responses unless enabled.

9. Offline Post Recovery

Even if the platform goes down, KeeperVault stores all your drafts, logs, timestamps, and metadata offline ‚Äî giving you proof, recovery ability, and legal defense if needed.

10. Campaign Timeline Builder

Plan, stage, and preview major campaigns with nested timelines, asset attachments, collaborator notes, and approval checklists. Ideal for product launches, holiday campaigns, or multi-week story arcs.

